Class ReviewFeedback

java.lang.Object
questions.util.ReviewFeedback
public class ReviewFeedback extends Object
This file contains the class that shows the feedback left on a review by a student feedback id, the review that has feedback, the student who gave the feedback, and the text of the feedback
